}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== "21514P1320A"... + "Rev:A1 2012/06/28" is silkscreened on the main board in the FCC photos. Cameo is presumed to be the OEM.
A sticker with "UT38170 Rev.B" + "UMEC1226G" is on the power supply module in the FCC photos.
Default settings are per the FCC manual.
